<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - BlackMamba</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/htmx.org@1.9.10"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/hyperscript.org@0.9.12"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <%- partial('layouts/header') %>
    
    <main class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>Welcome to <%= title %></h1>
            <p class="lead">Your BlackMamba HTMX application is running!</p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>ðŸš€ Ready to Code</h3>
                    <p>Your project structure is set up with all BlackMamba patterns.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>ðŸ¤– Agent System</h3>
                    <p>AI agents are configured in <code>.opencode/agent/</code> directory.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <h3>âš¡ HTMX Powered</h3>
                    <p>HTMX and hyperscript are included for modern web interactions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="actions">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" hx-get="/health" hx-target="#status">
                    Check Health Status
                </button>
                <div id="status" class="mt-3"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps mt-5">
            <h2>Next Steps</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Review the generated project structure</li>
                <li>Set up your database: <code>npm run prisma:migrate</code></li>
                <li>Create your first feature: <code>blackmamba-agent new-feature todos</code></li>
                <li>Start building your application!</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <%- partial('layouts/footer') %>
</body>
</html>